1999-07-27  Robert Bihlmeyer  <robbe@orcus.priv.at>

	* Makefile.am (agent_SOURCES): Add "secmem.c", "i18n.h", "memory.h".
	(client_SOURCES): Add "i18n.h".

	* client.c (main): Exit on agent_init() failure.

